          "alignment": "Chaotic evil",
          "type": "Giant",
          "name": "Young Forest Oni",
          "description": "Standing over nine feet tall, this hunch-backed giant has dusky red skin mottled with bark-like scars. Its wild black hair falls in tangles around two short horns. It wears rough leather strips and carries a massive spiked kanabo over its shoulder.",
          "lore": "Born of a fleeting union between a restless mountain spirit and a wandering oni, the Young Forest Oni prowls the ancient woods of Rokugan, its eyes alight with primal hunger. Though not yet fully grown, it wields the spiked kanabo with deadly vigor, terrorizing woodcutters and lone travelers. Local legends speak of its laughter echoing through mist-shrouded groves just before a brutal ambush."
